{"tid":1725982,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警疑蓄意向滅火消防擲催淚彈","createTime":"2019-11-16T03:05:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T03:29:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6ea1cc23cd98fe95bbfd353e1bb172e0ace35444","tid":1725982,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T03:05:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191116/NV7SK435XUTFUAOIYNUP3ANLVA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191116%2FNV7SK435XUTFUAOIYNUP3ANLVA%2F&d=1ryX%2BwltUSTIgmnFzyWg%2BAwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=0f04bb3c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191116%2FNV7SK435XUTFUAOIYNUP3ANLVA%2F&h=9647f092\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191116/NV7SK435XUTFUAOIYNUP3ANLVA/</a><br />\n<br />\n警疑蓄意向滅火消防擲催淚彈<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191116/large/1573835115_f233.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191116%2Flarge%2F1573835115_f233.jpg&h=43b68ea4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n三名消防員在旺角救火期間，催淚彈突然落在身旁。now電視畫面<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】反送中運動持續多月，社會衝突頻生，但在拯救生命最前線的消防和救護人員，卻屢受警暴阻撓，雙方更多次口角和衝突，更有消防員因消防車被警方催淚彈擊中上前投訴時，反遭警員喝罵、大力推撞及包圍；消防高層曾發稿以「誤會」淡化前線遭受的警暴，其後亦有指引呼籲屬員不要與警員爭辯。不過，昨日多區衝突中，再有消防員執勤滅火時，被警員用催淚彈幾乎擲中，需要慌忙走避，片段在網上廣傳，警員行為再度被指針對消防。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：恒久警惕是正當抗爭的代價<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網民揶揄：電光火石間睇錯<br />\n<br />\n根據片段顯示，凌晨時分多名消防員正在旺角彌敦道拖喉灌救馬路上的雜物火種，多名記者則在行人路上拍攝，現場亦未見任何示威者。在毫無警告廣播及黑旗下，突然後方遠處相距約數十米外有一枚催淚彈投擲至消防員附近，消防員即時停止灌救離開閃避，現場頓時被催淚煙籠罩，濃煙密佈。<br />\n<br />\n有關片段及圖片隨即廣傳，大量網民炮轟警員再次針對消防員攻擊，認為警方是特意將催淚彈射到消防員附近，亦有人用藍絲口吻模仿警方的解釋作揶揄：「因為電光火石間警察可能睇錯，我亦都聽唔到睇唔到唔知道。」<br />\n<br />\n■記者譚美芳"},{"pid":"35df65448dfea10e6bf89d23b11e410c24394891","tid":1725982,"uid":177047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T03:08:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"48f980fdcfd9e18e59e96f65155454eb48d82d57","tid":1725982,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T03:25:32.000Z","msg":"消防 under popo"},{"pid":"9995f4ad450348873297ce2120d41b9ba44c8f46","tid":1725982,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T03:25:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"faa883806d810fb93e86eddbf04339857e8e620a","tid":1725982,"uid":214173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T03:26:48.000Z","msg":"渣槍嗰個想點射都得,你咬佢食呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05e1274be619747daff02bcc969e962823bdbfd9","tid":1725982,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T03:27:50.000Z","msg":"二噁英?<br />\n不能只有我食到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0ec179ed4a9cb57a5389e74c49b88817530195f","tid":1725982,"uid":273716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T03:29:11.000Z","msg":"副處長都話消防係警察隻狗，比狗更賤既狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}